<TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="250">
<FONT CLASS="text10bold">Yellow</FONT><BR>
Sweet, with slightly firm, creamy flesh, our ripe yellow bananas are ready to eat the moment you get them. They will keep for two to three days at room temperature. Refrigerating bananas makes their skin turn dark brown &#151; but it slows ripening.<BR><BR></TD>
