<TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="250">
<FONT CLASS="text10bold">Half Yellow</FONT><BR>
Firm, with green-tinged ends and a unique, refreshing flavor, half-ripe bananas hold their shape during cooking. Ripen them to your liking for two to four days at room temperature. For speedier results, ripen them in a paper bag.<BR><BR>
</TD>
