<TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="250">
<FONT CLASS="text10bold">Green</FONT><BR>
With vibrant green peels, our unripe bananas will mature in four to six days at room temperature. To hasten ripening, place in a paper bag with a ripe apple in a warm, dry area &#151; avoid placing the bag in direct sunlight.<BR>
